// prose.jsonl — hand-curated ground truth for the prose corpora.
// Each line: {"corpus":"<name>","query":"<natural-language>","expected":"<file.md>#<heading-slug>"}.
// The expected key matches the prose-corpus doc-name produced by
// embedProseCorpus: <path-relative-to-corpus-root> + "#" + slugified H1/H2 heading.
// Slug rules: lowercase; runs of non-[a-z0-9] become single "-"; trim leading/trailing dashes.
// e.g. "## 1. Purpose" → "1-purpose"; "## Privacy & telemetry" → "privacy-telemetry".
//
// Comment lines (//) and blank lines are skipped by the loader.

